{"title":"如此“亲善访问”","authors":["池北偶　方成"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此“亲善访问”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　方成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总统要出使，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贩卖假友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前往南美洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有如临大敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大军保御驾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍旧怕有失，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备见元首。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先行搜官邸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严防有埋伏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以免遭行刺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到达各城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"极力藏行迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敢坐汽车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一律乘飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并非因路远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是怕西红柿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼克松尝过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在不是味。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然是如此，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必找苦吃。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}